query:
SELECT sc.id, sc.customerOrderNumber, sc.status, sc.createdAt,
       sci.id as itemId, sci.productSku, sci.productName, sci.expectedQuantity, sci.checkedQuantity
FROM stageChecks sc
LEFT JOIN stageCheckItems sci ON sc.id = sci.stageCheckId
WHERE sc.customerOrderNumber = 'PED-005'
ORDER BY sc.id DESC, sci.productSku;
